of me here today ♪</i>

257
00:12:22.844 --> 00:12:24.822
<i>♪ I got to clean up
all the mess I made ♪</i>

258
00:12:24.846 --> 00:12:27.955
<i>♪ Plus. I told myself
that there'll be better days ♪</i>

259
00:12:28.107 --> 00:12:29.365
