260
00:12:29.517 --> 00:12:31.086
<i>♪ I live today
like it's the final day ♪</i>

261
00:12:31.110 --> 00:12:32.368
<i>♪ Got to make a way ♪</i>

262
00:12:32.444 --> 00:12:34.962
<i>♪ And from the wave.
