266
00:12:41.546 --> 00:12:44.358
<i>♪ I feel it in my bloodstream ♪</i>

267
00:12:44.382 --> 00:12:47.383
<i>♪ I keep swimming upstream ♪</i>

268
00:12:47.535 --> 00:12:49.885
<i>♪ I'm running
