270
00:12:53.891 --> 00:12:56.484
<i>♪ I feel it in my bloodstream ♪</i>

271
00:12:56.561 --> 00:12:58.539
<i>SINGERS:
♪ Feel it in my bloodstream ♪</i>

272
00:12:58.563 --> 00:13:02.731
<i>♪ And I'm about
