279
00:13:18.733 --> 00:13:20.377
Oh.

280
00:13:20.401 --> 00:13:21.417
Okay.

281
00:13:21.569 --> 00:13:24.420
<i>(dramatic music)</i>

282
00:13:24.572 --> 00:13:30.351
