285
00:13:37.843 --> 00:13:41.565
<i>DEAN MARTIN:
♪ How lucky can one guy be? ♪</i>

286
00:13:41.589 --> 00:13:45.107
<i>♪ I kissed her.
and she kissed me ♪</i>

287
00:13:45.259 --> 00:13:47.404
<i>♪ Like the fella once said ♪</i>

288
00:13:47.428 --> 00:13:50.090
<i>♪ "Ain't that a kick
